6. Challenges and Mitigations

Challenge Mitigation
In‑flight quantum processor cooling Ruggedised cryocooler; classical fallback for optimisation.
Morphing wing reliability Redundant actuators; extensive fatigue testing; health monitoring.
Ethical AI misjudgment Formal verification; human‑in‑the‑loop; independent red team.
Cybersecurity Quantum encryption; hardware root of trust; continuous monitoring.
Sensor fusion in dense clutter Diverse sensors; extensive training with synthetic data.
Ramjet ignition at altitude Redundant igniters; windmill restart capability.
