7. Ethical and Regulatory Considerations

The HDMI is designed from the ground up to respect international humanitarian law. The TRIAD AI layer (Michael) ensures that every engagement is proportional, distinguishes combatants from civilians, and minimises collateral damage. A human operator remains in the loop for any lethal action, with the AI providing recommendations and explanations.

The system will undergo rigorous independent ethical auditing and will be fielded only after approval from national and international bodies. Its nuclear intelligence layer (QNI) includes additional safeguards to prevent accidental engagement of nuclear threats.

